history.content:
Are you looking to make an impact at Berkeley? Interested in CyberSecurity? Want to learn more about CyberSecurity? 

 

Become an executive officer for WiCyS @ CAL, the brand new UC Berkeley chapter of national non-profit WiCyS (www.wicys.org)! 

 

Women in CyberSecurity at Berkeley is looking for executive officers!

All genders and backgrounds welcomed! All skill levels invited! Looking for an enthusiastic team for the Fall! 

 

Open Positions:

  • Secretary

  • Finance Lead

  • Faculty & Corporate Relations Lead

  • WebDev Lead

  • Social Lead

  • Publicist

  • Technical Training Team Lead

 

Information about each position can be found here: https://tinyurl.com/WiCySRoles

 

Apply here: https://tinyurl.com/applytoWiCyS

Deadline: 8/21/2020 1:00 PM PST. 

Email wicyscal@gmail.com if you have any questions.
